{"tid":106970,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"果斷刪咗周興哲版《以後別做朋友》","createTime":"2017-02-04T06:07:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-05T16:13:37.000Z","uid":41237,"like":7,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"732bb7b20bd326f8516bf522358142bd19a4384b","tid":106970,"uid":41237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T06:07:37.000Z","msg":"本身係冇聽過呢首歌嘅 又冇睇齣劇<br />\n係聽蕭敬騰夢想的聲音唱先知<br />\n一聽到即刻覺得好震撼 點解咁好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n電腦Loop咗都好幾日<br />\n<br />\n但係手機出街一路都冇得聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n於是今日錯手down咗周興哲版本聽<br />\n起碼聽過 兩個比較公平啲呀嘛<br />\n結果覺得呢個所謂音樂才子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唱得氣若游絲 雞仔聲 高音唔入心入肺<br />\n<br />\n當然音樂呢啲好主觀啊 我都明<br />\n我就係鍾意蕭敬騰呢嘅版本都冇辦法<br />\n可能好似食嘢咁 食完鹹野覺得啲淡野冇味<br />\n<br />\n唔知各位巴絲又點睇呢<br />\n正皮 - 蕭敬騰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n負皮 - 周興哲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"742efaaa5291d1063c7a3c3721543090bcf58998","tid":106970,"uid":13718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T06:23:15.000Z","msg":"一定係老蕭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"197c1eeb4a446d0e58db4e56bf72799d6e8177fa","tid":106970,"uid":41237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T08:09:45.000Z","msg":"冇正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30c0760b1910632f20b0133d724cfbb8a65ae3fb","tid":106970,"uid":75605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T16:13:37.000Z","msg":"俾負皮肯定無聽過雨神版本<br />\n雨神翻唱之神，可惜唔似姐撚 jj 香港唔紅"}]}